}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite journal|last1=Gerstenfeld|first1=Phyllis B.|last2=Grant|first2=Diana R.|last3=Chiang|first3=Chau-Pu|title=Hate Online: A Content Analysis of Extremist Internet Sites|journal=Analyses of Social Issues and Public Policy|volume=3|pages=29|year=2003|doi=10.1111/j.1530-2415.2003.00013.x}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;br /&gt;[[Euroscepticism]]
